For use it : 
command : npm install

For the backend : 
command : nodemon server

For the frontend : 
command : npm run start

///////////////////////////////////////
This project is a site with many quiz about a lot of theme like : 
-history
-French language
-mangas
-pop culture
-etc

You can see them on home page and select one.
After this select, you can choose a difficulty (easy, normal, hard)
And you can access quiz

if you want save your progress, create an account and see on your profil all tests you passed and their results
///////////////////////////////////////
I use Sass for stylesheet